Package: ggpicrust2
Type: Package
Title: Make Picrust2 Output Analysis and Visualization Easier
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Chen(Caffery) Yang
Maintainer: Chen(Caffery) Yang <cafferychen7850@gmail.com>
Description: The ggpicrust2 package makes it easy to analyze and visualize Picrust2 output. It offers pre     -defined plots and functions to generate statistical plots about microbiome functional predictions,      as well as customization options. Plus, with its one-click feature to generate publication-level         plots, you can save time and create professional-grade figures with ease. Try the ggpicrust2 package     to streamline your Picrust2 analysis and visualization process.
